Good Afternoon Richard,

I have completed a review for the request for temporary accommodation and w=
ould not be able to get this approved for you.

As originally discussed, the policy limit is outlined in the policy and is =
not usually something that can be exceeded.  I did complete a review of the=
 claim to see if there were any exceptional circumstances that could be con=
sidered, however have been unable to identify any grounds to request an ext=
ension.

Please see the attached letter formally outlining my response to this reque=
st.  This letter includes a breakdown of the progression of the claim, as w=
ell as the steps taken by Tower to progress this claim.

Kind Regards


[cid:image002.jpg@01DC6DC7.ACA694F0]
