k-word">
<div class=3D"WordSection1">
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Good Afte=
rnoon Richard,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">I have co=
mpleted a review for the request for temporary accommodation and would not =
be able to get this approved for you.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">As origin=
ally discussed, the policy limit is outlined in the policy and is not usual=
ly something that can be exceeded.&nbsp; I did complete a review of the cla=
im to see if there were any exceptional circumstances
 that could be considered, however have been unable to identify any grounds=
 to request an extension.&nbsp;
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Please se=
e the attached letter formally outlining my response to this request.&nbsp;=
 This letter includes a breakdown of the progression of the claim, as well =
as the steps taken by Tower to progress this
 claim. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US">Kind Rega=
rds <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-fareast-language:EN-US"><o:p>&nbs=
p;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"mso-ligatures:standardcontextual"><o:=
p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
