<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ar=
ial&quot;,sans-serif">Good afternoon Grant,</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ar=
ial&quot;,sans-serif">&nbsp;</span><o:p></o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ar=
ial&quot;,sans-serif">Thanks for your email below. My client does not accep=
t that this scope includes all the necessary work to reinstate the fire dam=
age at her house. However, in order to keep this
 claim moving towards resolution, please proceed to cost Tower=E2=80=99s sc=
ope of works as you suggest.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span style=3D"font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Ar=
ial&quot;,sans-serif">My client=E2=80=99s experts will review the scope and=
 repair methodology and we will revert. Due to the time of year, this will =
not be until late January. Some issues which we require
 expert input on include:</span><o:p></o:p></p>
