<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good=
 morning Raffaella, Richard &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Plea=
se find attached the following documents for your review:<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l4 level1 lfo2"><span lang=
=3D"FR" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Combustion pre-decontamination survey [ =
