<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi S=
tephen,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Belo=
w is a copy of an email which I sent to all parties this afternoon outlayin=
g the expected time frames of the results which will be available to be sha=
red with all regarding test results from
 23 Mays Street, Devonport.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p=
>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prio=
r to receiving the report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to =
take whatever steps I can to progress the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prel=
iminary results and findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete=
 understanding of what the final scope of works will be to fully remediate =
the property under the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p=
>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If w=
e accept on a preliminary basis that the scope of works required to remedia=
te the property is
<b><u>generally defined</u></b> as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p=
>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">B=
asement Level</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span lang=
=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all exposed i=
nternal brick surfaces to ground level of dwelling<o:p></o:p></span></li><l=
i class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span lang=
=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace charred timber framework to m=
idfloor structure and ground floor walls as required<o:p></o:p></span></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 level1 lfo3"><span lang=
=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rebuild rear deck and steps to match =
existing
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 =
level1 lfo3"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace all ha=
rdwood decking boards to internal balcony
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l0 =
level1 lfo3"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and enca=
psulate all timber structural components to ground-floor walls and midfloor=
