<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good=
 afternoon Raffaella &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I ha=
ve just spoken with Abigail Collin re the forthcoming test results.<o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We e=
xpect the test results to be available to share with all parties by the end=
 of next week. I have chased the provider to expedite this.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The =
preliminary report from the Forensic Testing will contain the =E2=80=98raw =
data=E2=80=99 from the laboratory results, and the locations of the sample =
sites from where the tests were conducted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As p=
romised this preliminary report will be shared with all as soon as it is re=
ceived and it will be followed by a fuller report which will provide Towers=
 position on the findings of the report.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Than=
k you for your continued patience.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rega=
rds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Gran=
t. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p=
