<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:=
white">Kia ora Grant, Thank you for your email and for confirming receipt o=
f our letter. Friday, 17 October after 2:</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=
=3D"font-size:1.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,sans-serif;color:white">=
=E2=80=8A</span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:white">=
00
 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment c=
ould be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><=
span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:=
white">&nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Kia ora Grant,<o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thank you for your email and fo=
r confirming receipt of our letter.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 p=
m works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment cou=
ld be scheduled accordingly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I also reserve my right to unde=
rtake independent testing and assessment of the property to ensure a full a=
nd impartial evaluation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Having reviewed the proposed pl=
an, I=E2=80=99m concerned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. =
It does not include the first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, =
and the basement coverage seems partial, given
 the known extent of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I therefore request confirmatio=
n that the planned inspection and sampling will be expanded to include all =
levels and relevant structural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that To=
wer will meet my reasonable costs should
 I need to arrange independent specialists to carry out supplementary testi=
ng (including laboratory analysis).<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please confirm the final timing=
 for the 17th and the revised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></=
span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Ng=C4=81 mihi,<o:p></o:p></span=
></p>
</div>
