<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Than=
k you for the letter received yesterday at 4:35</span><span lang=3D"EN-US">=
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am=
 replying to acknowledge receipt of the letter, and to further acknowledge =
that Abigail will be copied into all correspondence moving forward.</span><=
span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I ha=
ve requested that the appointed specialists provide dates and times when th=
ey can be available.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
